title: Nordo in for PA #92Noon! Fuller/Bercich/Gleeman/Charchian
description: Eric Nordquist is back in the big chair filling in for Paul Allen! Marcus Fuller calls in to talk Gophers hoops, Vikings Radio Analyst Pete Bercich previews the border battle, Aaron Gleeman is in studio to talk Twins and, believe it or not, Spring Training, and Paul Charchian checks in to talk fantasy football and more!
